snippet.title: RoboSquad Revolution | Gameplay Trailer | Early Access | Nov 2023
snippet.description:
RoboSquad Revolution Open Beta kicks off on Steam and Epic Games in November, 2023. Make sure to hit subscribe to receive news on the Revolution.

Welcome to the Revolution, where you are an insurgent robot marching to the beat of your own motherboard in the name of rebellion. Level up your components and rewrite the future of AI, one Hologram Throwdown at a time. Well what are you waiting for, metalhead? Join a squad for free today!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/RoboSquadRevolt
Discord:  https://discord.gg/robosquad
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2363620/RoboSquad_Revolution_Early_Access/
Epic Games: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/zorans-resistance-2bc134
Find out More: https://www.zorans.com/
